283
00:10:45.095 --> 00:10:46.135
Ahora te lo confieso,

284
00:10:46.589 --> 00:10:49.069
porque dios ha permitido que las cosas tomen

285
00:10:49.069 --> 00:10:49.949
repentinamente

286
00:10:49.949 --> 00:10:51.070
mejor rumbo,

287
00:10:51.389 --> 00:10:52.269
y también

288
00:10:52.509 --> 00:10:54.350
