524
00:20:11.940 --> 00:20:12.900
matrimonio por amor,

525
00:20:13.685 --> 00:20:16.565
pero Dunia no es tan solo una muchacha

526
00:20:16.565 --> 00:20:17.445
inteligente,

527
00:20:17.845 --> 00:20:20.005
